through hospital services","Legal and accessible via telehealth up to 63 days gestation","Restricted to metropolitan areas only","Limited to registered obstetricians and gynaecologists"],"correctOptions":[2],"correctResponses":null,"explanation":"\u003Cp\u003EMS-2 step is indicated, \u003Cstrong\u003Elegal and accessible for medical abortion up to 63 days gestation\u003C/strong\u003E. Healthcare providers who complete required training can provide medical abortion services, including via telehealth consultations.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThe incorrect options can be explained:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ERequires consultation with two doctors before 22 weeks\u003C/strong\u003E is incorrect; a single qualified healthcare provider can prescribe medical abortion before 22 weeks gestation.\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EAvailable only through hospital services\u003C/strong\u003E is also false, as medical abortion can be provided through various healthcare settings including primary care.\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003EWhilst some regional, rural and remote areas have difficulties accessing abortion care, it is not legally \u003Cstrong\u003Erestricted to those in metropolitan areas\u003C/strong\u003E.\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ELimited to registered obstetricians and gynaecologists \u003C/strong\u003Eis incorrect - appropriately trained general practitioners can provide medical abortion services and have a particularly important role in the provision of early abortion care.\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003EMedical abortion services are regulated under state and territory legislation but are legal throughout Australia. Healthcare providers must complete specific training to prescribe abortion medications. The 63-day gestational limit for telehealth medical abortion is based on evidence regarding safety and effectiveness of the medication combination.\u003C/p\u003E","optionExplanations":["","","","",""],"learningPoints":["Medical abortion using mifepristone and misoprostol is safe and effective up to 63 days (9 weeks) gestation.","Access to abortion services is protected under Australian law in all states and territories.","Telehealth consultations are a valid pathway for medical abortion services in Australia."],"references":["Termination of pregnancy. Queensland Health. Available from: https://www.health.qld.gov.au/__data/assets/pdf_file/0029/735293/g-top.pdf","Clinical guideline for abortion care. RANZCOG. Available from: https://www.racgp.org.au/getmedia/a5c4f797-9b8c-4b0f-a9db-c41a0486bb97/Clinical-Guideline-for-Abortion-Care.pdf.aspx"]},"relationships":{"itemRevision":{"data":{"type":"itemRevisions","id":"56329"}},"question":{"data":{"type":"questions","id":"17465"}},"stemMedia":{"data":[]},"explanationMedia":{"data":[]}}},{"type":"itemRevisions","id":"56329","links":{"self":"https://app.emedici.com/api/itemRevisions/56329"},"attributes":{"createdAt":"2024-12-16T14:47:42+10:30","updatedAt":"2024-12-16T14:49:53+10:30"},"relationships":{"item":{"data":{"type":"items","id":"10155"}},"content":{"data":{"type":"questionRevisions","id":"70862"}}},"meta":{"canDelete":false}},{"type":"tags","id":"67","links":{"self":"https://app.emedici.com/api/tags/67"},"attributes":{"emoji":"","name":"Basic Science","synonyms":null,"description":null,"position":null,"createdAt":null,"updatedAt":null},"relationships":{"group":{"data":{"type":"tagGroups","id":"5"}},"heading":{"data":null}},"meta":{"itemCount":0}},{"type":"tags","id":"71","links":{"self":"https://app.emedici.com/api/tags/71"},"attributes":{"emoji":"","name":"Junior","synonyms":null,"description":"Suitable for a junior, pre-clinical medical student","position":0,"createdAt":null,"updatedAt":null},"relationships":{"group":{"data":{"type":"tagGroups","id":"6"}},"heading":{"data":null}},"meta":{"itemCount":0}},{"t